"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"[![Nine Chronicles](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*54NhxLD2E5\\\\_WayA07UyDJA.png)](https://ninechronicles.medium.com/?source=post_page-----dba078b0f602--------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*K7tr_mqRTiNRCoCkeoLsng.png)\\n\\nDear Adventurers, **Arena Season 0** has just started and we witnessed a lot of fights full of bloodshed in the past week. Today closes the first week of Season 0 and we are happy to share some of the news and interesting moments from it.\\n\\nJoin the player vs player mode and challenge yourself against other players!\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0\\\\*rDJ4AQQXvliQDPoK)\\n\\n## üòâ **Arena at a glance:**\\n\\nAll of the players were fighting actively enough and definitely made sure all of their gear was polished and ready to go against the other players in the battles to the top.\\n\\nThis week, indeed, was very interesting and you all know that this is only the beginning! Here are some interesting stats along with the TOP 10 players who showed the greatest stamina this week. Ready?\\n\\n## **TOP 10 from Week 41 (First Week of Season 0)**\\n\\n1.  bluewrath #7F9E\\n2.  AndrewLW #49F9\\n3.  saranghaeyomilkis #1a15\\n4.  Farm4Ace #7d58\\n5.  yuzuppy #e647\\n6.  bmcdee #c30C\\n7.  EGLD #2A17\\n8.  sauliooz #8993\\n9.  Yoink #d221\\n10. Wabbs #aB44\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*oGyaVjAqllZDP2boLB8KNA.png)\\n\\nEach of the players would be rewarded 1600 NCG\\n\\nYou may also check the ranking right here at <https://onboarding.nine-chronicles.com/arena/season/0>\\n\\nTo sum up all things together, there were** 171134 **total arena battles, and **2962** participants within the first week of the season. Amazing start of the week!\\n\\nThe [**Arena Season 0**](https://ninechronicles.medium.com/announcing-nine-chronicles-arena-season-0-896k-ncg-prize-pool-season-exclusive-nfts-%EF%B8%8F-ce0b12bc7e08) will finish on **2,463,999**th block **119,857** blocks away within 2 weeks and a half, a little earlier than expected. Those who haven‚Äôt tried the Arena yet, grab your best gear and join the battlefield. It will definitely be fun!\\n\\nLast but not least, the sweetest things are yet to come! This season‚Äôs exclusive and rare **NFT**s are waiting for the top Arena NCG stakers!\\n\\nFinally, please remember that:\\n\\n‚ÄúDuring the **Arena Season 0**, only one character from each account will be able to participate in earning bonus **NCG** reward.‚Äù\\n\\nWhat happens if players fight with more than one character from the same account in the Arena?\\n\\nThe highest ranked avatar will be considered for the rewards, meaning the best one among those 3 characters gets the reward.\\n\\n‚ÅâÔ∏è The **Arena Season 0** rewards will be distributed through the [Play2Earn](https://onboarding.nine-chronicles.com/) portal thus, it‚Äôs highly recommended to all of the users to be registered in the portal before the Arena Season 0 finishes!\\n\",\"timestamp\":1633849989,\"title\":\"Nine Chronicles Arena Season 0 ‚Äî First Week‚Äôs Update\"},\"digest\":\"is-5pdFha5e0A2XL1gHFyNwDiF7gnhMYffOviwuXPNQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x8f32844357f27d8C185255832B914dd7E3eCFB9a\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"A_OAag0thieGZQa5sf3r7R4DFyhHx0ARPTKmPMZx5uE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"tChAl9bLhE03juj_KVnbGsbWCYMm_Cmrl8C1-KZ9-Ls\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"FrgN6fUDXD1a82EUTfLTnuwz3SCjOKXqWp_NGu3bJ6rldkXaEg4D8EYVwaXcVu7adVEewuKoXKu4sxAWNIE-Rg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc3ab87be512f745e4d2c4bd7f79ce448be458ba5d9337a2b1067623725d77e8b3051fa475eb326f475320031073767da9861d017470af7e188041c289f5a2e321c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"A_OAag0thieGZQa5sf3r7R4DFyhHx0ARPTKmPMZx5uE\\\",\\\